ENTRIES1.title: Aon Risk Reward Challenge
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Season-long Aon Risk Reward Challenge will highlight the world’s best professional golfers

ENTRIES1.title: Cambia Fan Pavilion
ENTRIES1.subtitle: The Cambia Fan Pavilion is located near the Main Entrance and is open throughout the day, Thursday – Sunday featuring displays and free samples courtesy of participating tournament sponsors.

ENTRIES1.title: Food Carts
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Portland’s finest Food Carts are located at the Driving Range and #17 Green. The featured food carts on the driving range are: Koi Fusion, Slick’s BBQ, Dutch Brothers Coffee, Beer Garden. On the 17th Green you can find a smaller version of our Beer Garden along with the Smack Dabs food cart.

ENTRIES1.title: BYOB
ENTRIES1.subtitle: Bring Your Own Bottle! In an effort to reduce our carbon footprint, please support us going green and bring a reusable water bottle to the tournament! Stations will be located near the driving range, Cambia Fan Pavilion, the Pro Shop, 12 green, 12 tee / 3 green and 17 green.
